metadata.name: Ventana Uno
metadata.description:
This is my tribute to those that regardless where life has taken you, you can still be happy and create your sanctuary. To Dominican Republic for being one of the most beautiful countries in the world and to CryptoArt for allowing me to share this when I most needed it. I hope this can bring a smile to your face every Monday when the skies are gray, when feeling stuck, lonely and alone or you're at the job you can't wait to leave.  
From my Ventana to yours.
